                     <interp inst="t17710911-33-person314" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known Castle ever since he was between six and seven years old; he was always an honest, sober lad. I lived next door seven years. He is a lighterman.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17710911-33-person315">
